Syntax and use

1) Declaration

name = Array.create(size)

All values of the array are set to a value.

2) Access

name[number]

3) Multi dimensional arrays

name = Array.create(2)
name[0] = Array.create(2)
name[1] = Array.create(2)

4) Other

Array starts at 0.

Implementation

name[0] =>
LOAD name
LOAD_CST
ARRAY_VAL

---> Load esl::Value* contains in case TOS1[TOS]

name[0] = 1 =>
LOAD_INT 1
LOAD name
LOAD_CST 0
ARRAY_VAL
STORE_STK

ARRAY_VAL =>

Push in the stack TOS1[TOS]

---

STORE_STK

Perform TOS = TOS1
Pop TOS, but not TOS1
